# @name createRouteContext2A
POST http://localhost:{{configPort}}/v2/dataStoreContexts
Authorization: bearer {{configToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dataStoreId": {{dataStore2Id}},
  "contextKey": "districtId",
  "contextValue": "{{districtId1}}"
}

### Create Route Context for Data Store 2 - schoolYear
# @name createRouteContext2B
POST http://localhost:{{configPort}}/v2/dataStoreContexts
Authorization: bearer {{configToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dataStoreId": {{dataStore2Id}},
